@node Preface
@chapter Preface

This manual describes Guile-SSH library which is aimed to provide
access to @acronym{SSH} protocol for GNU Guile programs.

The manual is partly based on libssh documentation.

@node Introduction
@chapter Introduction

Guile-SSH is a library that provides access to the @acronym{SSH}
protocol for programs written in
@url{https://www.gnu.org/software/guile/, GNU Guile} interpreter.  It
is a wrapper to the underlying @url{http://www.libssh.org/, libssh}
library.

